				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: fear kite training <a name="5682"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 25 03 10:30 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span> I just remembered where I used it in my 20s.  I fear kited Aviaks in South karana.  I know, everybody has been there before but it is the perfect place to fear kite.  Easy to get single pulls with lull, big running room with nothing to agro on you, when things go light blue you just pick the next higher bird type, and it is relatively uncamped now so you have the run of everything from the ground level up.  
<br />

<br />
Nonstop action with some decent gems drops.  You can also sell to the stuck-up bird at the top of the nest if you sneak up on him.   And just in case you have never been there, the birds never go KoS on you, no matter how many you kill.  Even more....With all the room to run around, you can practice every type single strategy at your disposal on these guys and selo to the nearby zone if it goes bad.
<br />

<br />
It never gets any easier than this.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
