			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Before you start fear kiting, make sure that your brass instrument skill is fairly close to all of your other instrument skills.
<br />

<br />
When I first got this song and tried to use it, if fizzled every 19 out of 20 tries.  This was because my brass skill was so much lower than all of my other instrument skills.  Thus I never used until I got the Haste song that uses brass and spent all day and night in the Bazaar singing to get Brass up to the appropriate level.</span></td>
