				<td colspan="2"><span>Brass is for the higher level haste songs, like Ervajs' and Rhondos, Maximus etc. (going from memory here).  
<br />

<br />
Careful using your AoE dot song in the bazaar, don't aggro anything with it and you'll be fine.
<br />

<br />
Yes you should miss notes less often with higher skills in your song classes.  That being said, I think our casting was nerfed with LoY so we fizzle way too much now even with maxed song skills.
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps,
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
